title: BIG 10's Big Weekend
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and Rod Gilmore preview the upcoming Indiana at Ohio State game this weekend. The crew also discusses the implications of the Bedlam Series this year. Gilmore breaks down USC quarterback Kedon Slovis and Luginbill talks about the Florida Gator's passing game. Finally, the crew previews the Cincinnati and UCF game.
